Subject: License key not working
Description:
I have a an auditor's license which is suppose to expire in January 2025. However I've downloaded the latest 3.1.0.01 and the license no longer works. The software reports that the software is unsupported since 27-1-2023. When I load 3.2.0.1 with the same key it works fine. 

Do i need a new license key? I can supply current key if needed..
Solution_Comment__c:
Issue: same as initial.

Solution: asked for the license key and it was incorrect. Involved AO to generate new license - all worked
